        "text": "Analyze this construction site photo in detail. Identify:\n1. Visible construction activities and work being performed\n2. Progress status and completion stage\n3. Materials visible on site\n4. Machinery and equipment present\n5. Workforce activity level\n6. Safety observations (PPE usage, barriers, signage)\n7. Possible next work stages based on current progress\n8. Any visible issues, delays, or risks\n\nProvide a professional, factual analysis.",
